  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CloseableJobListener
    Extension of JobListener that also extends Closeable.
    JobLauncher
    An interface for classes that launch a Gobblin job.
    JobListener
    An interface for classes used for callback on job state changes.
    JobLock
    A class for claiming exclusive right to proceed for each scheduled run of a job.
    Limiter Deprecated
    This class has been moved to Limiter.
    TaskStateTracker
    An interface for classes that track TaskStates.

    AbstractJobLauncher
    An abstract implementation of JobLauncher that handles common tasks for launching and running a job.

    A builder class for BoundedBlockingRecordQueue.

    FileBasedJobLock
    An implementation of JobLock that relies on new file creation on a file system.
    Fork
    A class representing a forked branch of operations of a Task flow.
    FsDatasetStateStore
    A custom extension to FsStateStore for storing and reading JobState.DatasetStates.

    TaskExecutor

    An extension to WorkUnitState with run-time task state information.
